    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i checked under the leaves and didnt really see much of anything, just some weird small marks. it's like they're scavenging something or just sucking the life out of it in some sneaky way. if it isn't obvious bugs like caterpillars, what else could be causing that kind of depletion?",
